{"tid":2180472,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"9成人答錯嘅IQ題","createTime":"2020-08-30T01:13:57.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-30T22:26:53.000Z","uid":32511,"like":1,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":44,"replies":[{"pid":"b35980d2c3453a4f04f1e08b5978dd526c6f222b","tid":2180472,"uid":32511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-30T01:13:57.000Z","msg":"想像桌上有四張卡片<br />\n這副卡片 一面是數字 一面是顏色<br />\n而且有一個規則 :<br />\n如果卡片的一面是偶數 那另一面一定是紅色<br />\n四張卡片分別是 3 8 紅 棕<br />\n請問你至少要翻開哪幾張卡片 才能驗證這個規則是真的 ?<br />\n<br />\n第二題<br />\n <br />\n想像桌上有四張卡片<br />\n這副卡片 一面是飲用者的年齡 一面是一種飲料<br />\n而法律規定: 18歲以上才能喝酒<br />\n四張卡片分別是 23 啤酒 可樂 17<br />\n請問你至少要翻開哪幾張卡片 才能驗證酒吧老闆遵守法律?"},{"pid":"4036ae7141090fd69903cdee06be848990e87158","tid":2180472,"uid":251052,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-30T01:16:50.000Z","msg":"第一題 2張 8同棕"},{"pid":"444f81fa4aa7dc1621cd1b74b329fae054c19b1d","tid":2180472,"uid":54142,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-30T01:17:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5d54017bd1492337c75aa8aed3e1e648f0255818","tid":2180472,"uid":279400,"like":10,"dislike":2,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-30T01:19:02.000Z","msg":"第一題: 1 張 (8)<br />\n第二題: 2 張 (啤酒 17)"},{"pid":"f2c8df1f54786ec7376328be0fd3eef63e71426e","tid":2180472,"uid":10612,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-30T01:19:39.000Z","msg":"1.8<br />\n2.啤 17"},{"pid":"a429350107a3062a51c2e8d04b31668ff6ad08a3","tid":2180472,"uid":52760,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-30T01:20:54.000Z","msg":"1. 8同棕<br />\n2. 17同啤酒<br />\n利申：IQ80"},{"pid":"d29ad758986444cb3e16d76d463a7666a2662473","tid":2180472,"uid":212878,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-30T01:45:02.000Z","msg":"1. 3 張<br />\n2. 17 同啤"},{"pid":"055219bf025e17f5185730fe31fa4391214db651","tid":2180472,"uid":170782,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-