= 紅色係偶數<br />\n<br />\n第二條: 2張 (17同啤酒)<br />\n同第一題一樣theory<br />\n<br />\n利申: 冇腦嘅垃圾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e8ddcfd2da4a3c3367c7735220c260bc1b59ad1e","tid":2180472,"uid":134994,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-30T03:20:22.000Z","msg":"呢啲唔係叫邏輯題咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n1. 8<br />\n2. 啤酒 17"},{"pid":"040f1b973a18c65f5c8e4ab5e368013cd74e8848","tid":2180472,"uid":49893,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-30T03:21:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>第一題: 2張 (8同棕)<br />\n揭8證明偶數後面係紅色<br />\n揭棕證明上面嘅推論正唔正確<br />\n因為偶<span class=\"red\">數</span>係紅色 =/= 紅色係偶數<br />\n<br />\n第二條: 2張 (17同啤酒)<br />\n同第一題一樣theory<br />\n<br />\n利申: 冇腦嘅垃圾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"b0be7a174e591c0756075cbabd15db8ed942ff34","tid":2180472,"uid":22302,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"891336ddb9fcf1ae5a5d225218059e586b2612c8","tid":2180472,"uid":238747,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-30T02:07:07.000Z","msg":"第一題: 1 張 (8)。  （if even then red,no need check if red then even or odd)<br />\n第二題: 2 張 (啤酒 17)"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-30T03:22:02.000Z","msg":"棕都要揭開睇下係咪odd"},{"pid":"bc740c81c2473833caabcaeb23921de3668e71ee","tid":2180472,"uid":200529,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"444f81fa4aa7dc1621cd1b74b329fae054c19b1d","tid":2180472,"uid":54142,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-30T01:17:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-30T03:24:06.000Z","msg":"same as you"},{"pid":"47347596c653f4f7b4e70fd89408fa3e2aba93e7","tid":2180472,"uid":200529,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-30T03:25:20.000Z","msg":"9成人答錯有冇咁誇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e7b1ddfec4e78d829a7daee5d0f02bb2ae5e77f8","tid":2180472,"uid":271250,"like":6,"dislike":4,"score":2,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-08-30T03:51:21.000Z","msg":"諗咗先好睇我以下嘅嘢。<br />\n<br />\n呢兩題係想講：<br />\n（1）If A Then B = If not B Then not A  <br />\n（2）If A Then B &ne; If B Then A<br />\n（3）If A Then B &ne;If not A Then not B<br />\n<br />\n第一題偶數係A，紅色係B<br />\n第二題酒係A，18歲以上係B<br />\n<br />\n所以，呢兩題都需要開第二張同第四張。<br />\n<br />\n開第二張嘅原因直接；開第四張嘅原因係（1）；唔開第一張，第一題嘅原因係（3），第二題嘅原因係（2）；唔開第三張，第一題嘅原因係（2），第二題嘅原因係（3）。<br />\n<br />\n呢啲題目只係幾十年前小學升中要做嘅學能測驗黎，答得好就上Band one，答得唔好就上Band Five，所以如果答錯希望大家睇返啲教基本邏輯嘅教科書，因為呢種係培養獨立思考嘅必要條件嚟。我估樓主都係想大家咁樣做。"},{"pid":"999e683dbb274758ddb649361a9e78d9604dce39","tid":2180472,"uid":22231,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"47347596c653f4f7b4e70fd89408fa3e2aba93e7","tid":2180472,"uid":200529,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-30T03:25:20.000Z","msg":"9成人答錯有冇咁誇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-30T03:55:12.000Z","msg":"震驚60億人的事實"},{"pid":"bd2fdca2d5a448b9dd97c6d2911cfc41ea4f3383","tid":2180472,"uid":184509,"like":1,"dislike":8,"score":-7,"quote":{"pid":"e7b1ddfec4e78d829a7daee5d0f02bb2ae5e77f8","tid":2180472,"uid":271250,"like":6,"dislike":4,"score":2,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-08-30T03:51:21.000Z","msg":"諗咗先好睇我以下嘅嘢。<br />\n<br />\n呢兩題係想講：<br />\n（1）If A Then B = If not B Then not A  <br />\n（2）If A Then B &ne; If B Then A<br />\n（3）If A Then B &ne;If not A Then not B<br />\n<br />\n第一題偶數係A，紅色係B<br />\n第二題酒係A，18歲以上係B<br />\n<br />\n所以，呢兩題都需要開第二張同第四張。<br />\n<br />\n開第二張嘅原因直接；開第四張嘅原因係（1）；唔開第一張，第一題嘅原因係（3），第二題嘅原因係（2）；唔開第三張，第一題嘅原因係（2），第二題嘅原因係（3）。<br />\n<br />\n呢啲題目只係幾十年前小學升中要做嘅學能測驗黎，答得好就上Band one，答得唔好就上Band Five，所以如果答錯希望大家睇返啲教基本邏輯嘅教科書，因為呢種係培養獨立思考嘅必要條件嚟。我估樓主都係想大家咁樣做。"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-30T03:58:28.000Z","msg":"好撚叻呀😂"},{"pid":"dfbefee3c9bb0650b9085f0b0b5637b207313b69","tid":2180472,"uid":271250,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"bd2fdca2d5a448b9dd97c6d2